review:
OMG! The hardest quest in my life). 

I want more. I hope we'll see in the next part of the game:
1. more letters and sad stories;
2. more bald women and keyholes;
3. more tools (except a screwdriver), perhaps a hammer or even a bowl plunger;
4. more animated [strike]cats[/strike] pets or mice;
5. maybe some mushrooms? The "Death cap" or an "amanita"?

Nice game.
10 dead cats out of 10
